{"tid":2478834,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"再爆市民被打錯針 一家三口約科興變打復必泰","createTime":"2021-04-07T10:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T11:19:16.000Z","uid":106,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce8c616e90d9813c7716613592ceca98eeb163a","tid":2478834,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"繼早前一名患血癌外籍男預約復必泰後，去錯場館被打錯科興疫苗，再爆出有市民被「打錯針」。消息指，一名 47 歲女子及 2 名家人於 3 月 10 日，預約到天水圍天暉路體育館接種科興疫苗，卻錯赴提供復必泰疫苗的元朗體育館，但仍獲接種復必泰疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，涉事的 47 歲女子在接種疫苗後，再向職員確認所接種的疫苗種類，始發現自己「打錯復必泰」，但連她在內，一家三口都已接種第一劑疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》正向負責營運元朗體育館的醫管局及負責疫苗接種計劃的公務員事務局查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%86%8D%E7%88%86%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%A2%AB-%E6%89%93%E9%8C%AF%E9%87%9D-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%A3%E5%8E%BB%E9%8C%AF%E5%A0%B4%E9%A4%A8-%E9%A0%90%E7%B4%84%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E8%AE%8A%E6%89%93%E5%BE%A9%E5%BF%85%E6%B3%B0/?fbclid=IwAR3wm3hCauTMreAR94lcHHYpBzqbPnJ2IAusFQF7QxdUdMX9_DFf3ngYxvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB-%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%258C%25AF%25E9%2587%259D-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%258E%25BB%25E9%258C%25AF%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25B4%2584%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2588%2588%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%25BF%2585%25E6%25B3%25B0%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3wm3hCauTMreAR94lcHHYpBzqbPnJ2IAusFQF7QxdUdMX9_DFf3ngYxvI&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=a5b9826a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB-%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%258C%25AF%25E9%2587%259D-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%258E%25BB%25E9%258C%25AF%25E5%25A